      "name": "autonomous-dev",
      "source": "./plugins/autonomous-dev",
      "description": "Autonomous AI development system — continuously-running, self-improving development pipeline that receives product requests, decomposes them through PRD→TDD→Plan→Spec→Code, reviews at every gate, monitors production, and generates its own improvement PRDs.",
